OL,3,CEmma Willis, Josh Widdicombe and
OL,4,CJohannes Radebe announced as new
OL,5,CStrictly hosts
OL,7,FEmma Willis, Josh Widdicombe and
OL,8,FJohannes Radebe have been announced as
OL,9,Fthe new hosts of Strictly Come Dancing.
OL,11,FThe presenter, comedian and
OL,12,Fprofessional dancer will host the show
OL,13,Fas a trio in a first for the flagship
OL,14,Fentertainment programme.
OL,16,FThe news was shared on the show's
OL,17,FInstagram page with the caption: "It's
OL,18,Fofficial... September 2026."
