OL,3,CEmma Willis, Josh Widdicombe and
OL,4,CJohannes Radebe announced as new
OL,5,CStrictly hosts
OL,7,FThe trio will take over from Tess Daly
OL,8,Fand Claudia Winkleman, who announced
OL,9,Ftheir departure from the programme in
OL,10,FOctober 2025.
OL,12,FDaly, 56, presented the series
OL,13,Falongside the late Sir Bruce Forsyth
OL,14,Fwhen it launched in 2004 while
OL,15,FWinkleman, 54, fronted its weekday
OL,16,Fcompanion show, It Takes Two.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
