OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1779217874
OL,3,CEmma Willis, Josh Widdicombe and
OL,4,CJohannes Radebe announced as new
OL,5,CStrictly hosts
OL,7,FWinkleman eventually moved on to host
OL,8,Fthe Sunday night results show
OL,9,Falongside Daly and joined the main
OL,10,Fshow every Saturday from 2014, after
OL,11,FSir Bruce stepped down.
OL,13,FWillis, who has hosted shows including
OL,14,FBig Brother and Celebrity Big Brother,
OL,15,Fas well as Love Is Blind UK said:
OL,16,F"It's no secret that I'm a huge fan of
OL,17,FStrictly ` I've cheered and danced
OL,18,Falong from my sofa for years ` so to
OL,19,Fbe stepping into the Strictly ballroom
OL,20,Fis something I can't quite comprehend.
OL,26,@xD@AOU
