OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1779217874
OL,3,CEmma Willis, Josh Widdicombe and
OL,4,CJohannes Radebe announced as new
OL,5,CStrictly hosts
OL,7,F"It's impossible to fill the shoes
OL,8,Fthat Tess and Claudia have left behind
OL,9,F` two wonderful, iconic women who have
OL,10,Fbeen the beating heart of Strictly for
OL,11,Fso long."
OL,13,FWiddicombe said: "Dancing the
OL,14,FCharleston dressed as a penguin for
OL,15,Fthe 2024 Christmas Special of Strictly
OL,16,Fremains my career high point, so I am
OL,17,Fgiddy with excitement, honoured and a
OL,18,Flittle overawed to be given the chance
OL,19,Fto step into the biggest shoes in
OL,20,Ftelevision.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@ROU
