OL,3,CEmma Willis, Josh Widdicombe and
OL,4,CJohannes Radebe announced as new
OL,5,CStrictly hosts
OL,7,F"I adore Emma and Jojo and can't wait
OL,8,Fto spend my weekends with them. I'll
OL,9,Fdust off the penguin costume."
OL,11,FEarlier on Tuesday, Widdicombe was
OL,12,Fgrilled on Good Morning Britain about
OL,13,Fthe rumours and he was about to be
OL,14,Fannounced as new presenter on the
OL,15,Fdancing show and successfully avoided
OL,16,Fthe question when pressed by Susanna
OL,17,FReid.
OL,19,FHe suggested Reid and co-host Ed Balls
OL,20,Fwould make better hosts.
