OL,3,CEmma Willis, Josh Widdicombe and
OL,4,CJohannes Radebe announced as new
OL,5,CStrictly hosts
OL,7,FWatch Josh Widdicombe's full interview
OL,8,Fon Good Morning Britain
OL,10,FRadebe, who joined the show as a
OL,11,Fprofessional dancer in 2018, said: "To
OL,12,Fbe returning to Strictly Come Dancing
OL,13,Fin this new role is beyond anything I
OL,14,Fever imagined.
