OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1779217874
OL,3,CEmma Willis, Josh Widdicombe and
OL,4,CJohannes Radebe announced as new
OL,5,CStrictly hosts
OL,7,F"This show has always stood for joy,
OL,8,Fheart, and togetherness, and I feel
OL,9,Fdeeply honoured to now help carry that
OL,10,Fmagic forward. To do it alongside the
OL,11,Fformidable Emma Willis and the utterly
OL,12,Fbrilliant Josh Widdicombe makes it
OL,13,Feven more special."
OL,15,FZoe Ball recently confirmed she did
OL,16,Fscreen tests for the hosting job but
OL,17,Fdid not get it.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
