OL,3,CEmma Willis, Josh Widdicombe and
OL,4,CJohannes Radebe announced as new
OL,5,CStrictly hosts
OL,7,FResponding to the announcement Kate
OL,8,FPhillips, the BBC's chief content
OL,9,Fofficer, said: "Emma, Johannes and
OL,10,FJosh's chemistry is undeniable.
OL,12,F"There's been so much speculation and
OL,13,Fhype, so I'm relieved we can share the
OL,14,Fnews with the public at last! I'd like
OL,15,Fto thank all the brilliant people we
OL,16,Fsaw before making this tough decision."
